OL,4,CPret, McColls and Welcome Break in
OL,5,Cminimum wage fail
OL,6, Pret, McColls and Welcome Break are
OL,7, among almost 200 firms "named and
OL,8, shamed" by the government for not
OL,9, paying workers the minimum wage.
OL,11,FIn total, 191 companies investigated
OL,12,Fbetween 2011 and 2018 failed to pay
OL,13,F#2.1m to more than 34,000 workers.
OL,15,FThe businesses were made to pay back
OL,16,Fthe money as well as being fined #3.2m.
OL,18,FPret, McColls and Welcome Break said
OL,19,Fthe underpayments were historic errors
OL,20,Fand staff had been swiftly reimbursed.
